NAME
       showfont  - displays all characters in the current screen-
       font.


SYNOPSIS
       showfont


DESCRIPTION
       showfont  uses  successive  switches  of  the  Application
       Charset  Map  in 8-bit console-mode to have all 256 or 512
       characters in the current font displayed on the screen.


SEE ALSO
       consolechars(8).



